Hilton Worldwide plans to double the size of our overall presence throughout the Middle East and Africa in the coming years New properties will include hotels and resorts in popular tourist destinations and business centers throughout Saudi Arabia, United Arab Emirates, Iraq, Egypt, Lebanon, Nigeria, South Africa and other strategic locations. We invite you to join us in filling the Earth with the light and warmth of hospitality and helping our guests experience the world-class service for which Hilton Worldwide is known.
